  <description>
    <p>
      A powerful and beautiful desktop timer application built with Tauri 2.0.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Four working modes: Countdown, Clock, Stopwatch, Counter</li>
      <li>Flexible layouts: Four-grid, Left-right split, Top-bottom split, Fullscreen single</li>
      <li>Customizable appearance: 12 display colors, adjustable font size, light/dark theme</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts support</li>
      <li>Prevent system sleep during timing</li>
      <li>Audio and visual alerts</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
